name: Emma Hudsonf
introduction:
my name is Emma Hudson. In the spring of 2015, I had just graduated from Georgetown University, attending Columbia University in New York with an interested in science and technology. I wanted to make a difference in people's lives with my own amazing stories.
My love of video games and anime has made me an extremely popular personality on Facebook, Twitter and family-friendly forums.
My favorite thing about being a mom is seeing your kids grow up.
Came out as trans a couple of years ago and started looking for a partner to share my authentic gender expression.
